&lt;h2 id=&#34;the-lotus-pond&#34;&gt;The Lotus Pond&lt;/h2&gt;

&lt;p&gt;This was actually my second time visiting Kaohsiung, the first time was during (technically right after it ended) my really great summer school in 2014.
That trip involved A LOT of rain, and although people always tell me &amp;ldquo;IT NEVER RAINS IN KAOHSIUNG&amp;rdquo;, I am still to enjoy a rainless time in the Big Hero.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;So what I now will show involves secret footage of a younger (and I guess thinner?) me, my good friend Snow, who we met up with this time as well, and my excellent guide from that time Robert, taken from the &lt;a href=&#34;https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Qijin_District,_Kaohsiung&#34; target=&#34;_blank&#34;&gt;Cijin lighthouse&lt;/a&gt;:&lt;/p&gt;

